Package: arena2r
Type: Package
Title: Arena To R: Nice Plots and Outputs for Arena Simulation Software
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Pedro Nascimento de Lima
Maintainer: Pedro Nascimento de Lima <pedrolima.n@gmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Pedro", "Lima","Nascimento de", email = "pedrolima.n@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre")) 
Description: This package reads Arena CSV output files and generates nice tables and plots. It does what I think Process Analyzer should do better. Future versions might include validation tests, and an interative Shiny App.
